link":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-1bf","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/fasting-shield-from-al-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":4541,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Fasting is a shield from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, fasting is only a shield by which the servant seeks protection from the Hellfire.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 15264 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23320,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/25\/fasting-fortress-shield-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":4541,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Fasting is a fortress, shield for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 25, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield and a fortress among the fortresses of the believer. Every deed is for its companion, but Allah says: Except fasting, as it is for Me, and I will reward it.\u201d Source: Musnad\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28101,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/fasting-distances-hundred-years\/","url_meta":{"origin":4541,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Allah distances him from Hell by 100 years","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts a day in the way of Allah Almighty, Allah will distance him from Hell by a measure of one hundred years of travel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2254 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28099,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/fasting-distances-seventy-autumns\/","url_meta":{"origin":4541,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Allah delivers him from Hell by seventy autumns","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts a day in the way of Allah Almighty, by that day Allah will deliver his face from the Hellfire a distance of seventy autumns of travel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2244 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14768,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/29\/saved-hellfire-sawm-siyam\/","url_meta":{"origin":4541,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Every night people saved by fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has people He redeems at the time of breaking fast, and that is during every night.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1643 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28096,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/shield-damaged-gheebah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4541,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Sins of tongue damage fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu \u2018Ubaydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield, as long as you do not damage it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2235 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0